Item 2.02.  Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
On July 26, 2017, D.R. Horton, Inc. issued a press release announcing its
results and related information for its third quarter ended June 30, 2017 and
declaring its quarterly dividend. A copy of the press release is attached hereto
as Exhibit 99.1 and is incorporated by reference in its entirety into this
Item 2.02.
The information furnished in this Item 2.02 shall not be deemed "filed" for
purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended, or
otherwise subject to the liabilities of that section, nor shall such information
be deemed incorporated by reference in any filing under the Securities Act of
1933, as amended, except as shall be expressly set forth by specific reference
in such filing.
Item 9.01.  Financial Statements and Exhibits.
(d) Exhibit



99.1      Press Release dated July 26, 2017 related to the Company's results and
          related information for the third quarter ended June 30, 2017 and
          declaring its quarterly dividend.



