	Design Product Quality | D.R. Horton













































California > Design Product Quality

Share































 



















 











































HOUSES DESIGNED TO BE EFFICIENT AND FLEXIBLE, WITH
                                            INDUSTRY BEST PRODUCT
• REDUCED MAINTENANCE
With the design of the houses, both architecturally and structurally, held to high standards, a HomeSense home is designed and built to require less maintenance.
• MANUFACTURER’S WARRANTIES
As the nation’s largest builder 8 years in a row (as reported by Builder Magazine), D.R. Horton has negotiated purchasing programs and warranties with trusted manufacture'rs. As a HomeSense home-owner, you reap the benefits of those partnerships. 
• PROFESSIONAL GUIDED UPGRADES
HomeSense buyers go to Design Centers created exclusively to guide them through the option and upgrade selection process. Professionally-trained designers educate buyers on all aspects of personalizing their HomeSense homes. 
• LOWER COST OF OWNERSHIP
With the Design/Construction Methods reducing maintenance, superior manufacturers warranties’ and Pre-Active Design to make the house adaptable to adding upgrades, advancements in technology and energy efficiency, a HomeSense home saves money now, and will continue to save money in the future.








 


 






 







HomeSense program available at D.R. Horton communities in Los Angeles, Riverside, San Bernardino, Imperial, San Diego and Orange Counties. Not all features available on all homes; features subject to change. Some features are optional/upgrade items, which may be purchased for inclusion in the home at an additional cost. See a D.R. Horton sales agent for complete details. D.R. Horton Los Angeles Holding Company, Inc. - CA BRE License #01258550. 



Visit us at DRHorton.com/SoCal


























