D.R. Horton has more than 35 years of experience delivering new homes that are designed and built on a foundation of quality and value. We will work closely with you to find the perfect place in this exciting city, so whether you would like to be close to the bright lights of the bustling city or you prefer the quieter, relaxing areas around the outskirts of town, we can introduce you to some amazing communities.


Las Vegas New Homes for Sale
Our dedication to homebuyers and commitment to high-quality construction has earned us the top spot on the Builder 100 since 2002. We specialize in creating unique, modern home designs, and, here in Las Vegas, you’ll find a huge variety of homes that can meet your needs. These plans include:

     - 2 to 6 bedrooms
     - 1 to 4-car garages
     - 2 to 7 bathrooms
     - Single or multi-story floorplans
     - 1,100 to more than 7,000 square feet

You can find your dream Las Vegas luxury home or you can experience something more quaint and cozy if you prefer. These communities are close to great schools and parks, keep you close to all the conveniences of the city. Take a look at these new homes in Las Vegas and Henderson and find the one that is perfect for you.


Calling Las Vegas Home
While Las Vegas is famous for its tourist attractions, hotels, and casinos, those aren’t the only reasons so many people are moving to this wonderful city. The weather is warm all year, you’ll find some of the best golf courses in the country, and there are plenty of activities for a laid-back lifestyle. (You can find more information on making a smooth transition to the city here.) 
If you enjoy the excitement of the city, you can spend time exploring the hotels and high-end shops or enjoying the world-famous magic, dance, and comedy shows. There’s always something new happening in this city that locals can experience. Las Vegas is growing quickly, and we can help you find the perfect place in this dynamic environment.
Contact us to learn more about our new homes for sale in Las Vegas. We are here to help you find the best modern and luxury homes in the area.
