D.R. Horton Careers


Being America’s Builder is something that D.R. Horton takes to heart. Over thirty-five years ago Donald R. Horton had a vision of creating affordable new homes with uncompromising quality. Those values have been at the core of D.R. Horton as we’ve grown from a local builder to the nation's largest homebuilder by volume traded on the New York Stock Exchange (ticker: DHI). It takes many dedicated professionals working together to deliver quality homes to families nationwide. 

D.R. Horton has grown from building one home for one family, to building thousands of homes, one family at a time. Nationwide, we are building communities and helping local families achieve their dreams.


Working for D.R. Horton is more than just a job - it is a career where your skills and passion for delivering quality homes make a difference in our customers' lives.
























