Why Horton

Horton listens. We’re known for and value our close, collaborative, customer working relationships…engineers to engineers. The results are innovative and optimized solutions.

Learn More





About HortonFounded in 1951, Horton is the world’s leading provider of premium engine-cooling solutions for OEM applications and the aftermarket. Its customer-inspired innovations — including fans, fan drives and related components — can help products last longer, run quieter and consume less fuel.
