Why Choose a New Build in Atlanta, GA?  


D.R. Horton offers incredible quality, along with affordability and convenience in this beautiful area of Georgia.  


     - D.R. Horton has been named the #1 home builder in America for 15 years in a row .  
     - We have been building quality houses in top developments for more than 35 years .  
     - There are nearly 40 communities in the Atlanta metro area to choose a home in. No matter what you desire, we have something here for you.  


Your Atlanta House  

You will love living in D.R. Horton’s new homes for sale in Atlanta, GA filled with amenities in a variety of comfortable floor plans and designs.  


     - Enjoy beautifully landscaped developments with spacious condos near the city, townhomes, and houses with up to more than 4,200 sq. ft.  
     - These New Homes for Sale in Fulton County offer modern kitchens feature large islands, granite countertops and more.  
     - Live in master-planned communities filled with desirable amenities.  




Living Here  


Enjoy all of the small town charm that comes with living in many of Atlanta’s fine suburbs, while being close to the big city and the many conveniences that it offers.  


     - Atlanta experiences hot summers and warm winters.  
     - Residents can cheer on local professional teams like the Braves or the Falcons or side with one of the fames college teams, Georgia Tech or UGA.  
     - The city has many great restaurants, and the southern cooking is some of the finest.  
     - Atlanta is one of the friendliest places to be, even in the midst of the big city.  


More About Atlanta, GA 


Atlanta boasts small town charm in its outlying suburbs, but is widely recognized for the great lifestyle it has to offer and our homes here are near all the top things to do in Atlanta.  


     - The Huffington Post refers to Atlanta as “The Big American City You’ve Been Missing Out On.”  
     - Forbes Named Atlanta the #14 best place for business and careers.  
     - Atlanta is a great place for businesses according to the Metro Atlanta Chamber of Commerce.  


Find homes in Atlanta, GA to suit your lifestyle. Contact us today and we’ll walk you through the process of finding your dream house.




























