Consolidated Results:
•       Consolidated pre-tax income increased 17% to $444.5 million compared to
 $378.6 million.
•       Consolidated pre-tax income as a percentage of consolidated revenues was
        11.8% compared to 11.7%.
•  Net income increased 16% to $289.0 million compared to $249.8 million.
• Diluted earnings per share increased 15% to $0.76 compared to $0.66.
